room_title: Escape room "The Book of the Dragons" by Clever Fox in Temecula
room_description: You have been summoned by the Eldaf the Wise. He has employed you to sneak into the evil Wizards study, find The Book of the Dragons and return it to him so he can free the last living dragon from the clutches of Shadowmen. Once you enter the study, you will only have an hour until Shadowmen calls the Dragon to destroy you and the book!
